---
// About page: mission, the founder's real story (adapted from the
// founder's own LinkedIn writing), how-we-work principles, contact form.
// Multi-industry framing throughout. The founder note is first-person
// and true to the source; name + photo drop into the marked spot.
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
import ClientLogos from '../components/ClientLogos.astro';
import InlineCta from '../components/InlineCta.astro';
import SimpleForm from '../components/islands/SimpleForm.jsx';
import { withBase } from '../lib/url';
import { breadcrumbSchema } from '../lib/seo';
import Clock from '@lucide/astro/icons/clock';
import MessageSquare from '@lucide/astro/icons/message-square';
import Layers from '@lucide/astro/icons/layers';

const formFields = [
  { name: 'name', label: 'Full name', placeholder: 'Your name' },
  { name: 'email', label: 'Email', type: 'email', placeholder: 'you@business.com' },
  { name: 'business', label: 'Business name', placeholder: 'Your business', required: false, optional: 'optional' },
  { name: 'phone', label: 'WhatsApp number', type: 'tel', placeholder: '+91 98765 43210', required: false, optional: 'optional, for a faster reply' },
  { name: 'message', label: "What's the one thing holding your growth back right now?", type: 'textarea', placeholder: "Tell us honestly, we'll be honest back" },
];

const jsonLd = breadcrumbSchema([
  ['Home', '/'],
  ['About', '/about/'],
]);
---

<Base
  title="About | Click.n.likes"
  description="Nine years of building organic growth systems for businesses across industries - SEO and content that keep generating leads long after the spend stops. Built on fundamentals, not the algorithm update of the month."
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 -z-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-teal/[0.07] via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-[5vw] pt-16 pb-14 lg:pt-20">
      <p class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-teal/30 bg-teal/5 px-4 py-1.5 text-[13px] font-semibold text-navy">
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-teal"></span> About Click.n.likes
      </p>
      <h1 class="reveal-mask mt-5 max-w-3xl font-display text-[clamp(2.1rem,4.4vw,3.4rem)] leading-[1.08] font-bold text-navy">
        <span class="mask-line"><span>Growth that does not disappear</span></span>
        <span class="mask-line" style="--d:120ms"><span>the moment the budget does.</span></span>
      </h1>
      <p class="reveal mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-navy/70" style="--d:240ms">
        Click.n.likes is a full-stack organic growth agency for SaaS companies, manufacturers, legal and professional
        firms, D2C brands and local businesses. We build organic systems, SEO and content that keep generating leads
        long after the work is done, so growth compounds instead of resetting every time the ad spend pauses.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The founder's story -->
  <section class="border-t border-navy/10 bg-off">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-[5vw] py-16">
      <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.35fr_0.65fr] lg:items-start">
        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] text-navy/50 uppercase">Why this agency exists</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-[clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.4rem)] leading-[1.15] font-bold text-navy">
            Most businesses are renting their growth. We build the kind you own.
          </h2>
          <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-navy/75">
            <p>
              Nearly every business I have worked with started the same way: spending on ads, getting results, then
              spending more to hold on to those results, and quietly realising that the moment the budget stops,
              everything stops. That is not a growth strategy. That is a dependency.
            </p>
            <p>
              For the past nine years, I have helped businesses across industries break that cycle by building organic
              growth systems, SEO and content that keep generating leads long after the work is done. A legal services
              brand came to me struggling to generate consistent inbound leads; within three months, SEO was their most
              reliable source. An eCommerce brand wanted visibility beyond paid ads; within two months, their site was
              appearing directly in Google's AI answers, pulling traffic and leads from a channel their competitors had
              not even considered yet.
            </p>
            <p>
              Here is what makes the difference: I do not build strategies around the latest algorithm update or the
              trending tactic of the month. I build on fundamentals, how people actually search, how trust is actually
              built, and how content compounds over time. Algorithms change. Human behaviour does not. Strategies built
              on that foundation keep working regardless of what Google ships next.
            </p>
            <p>
              I will be upfront about one thing: organic growth is not instant. If you need leads next week, paid ads
              are your answer. But if you are ready to build something that does not vanish when the budget does, that
              is exactly what we do, always built around your specific business, never a template.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Founder note card. Drop the founder's name + photo into the marked spots. -->
        <aside class="reveal lg:sticky lg:top-24" style="--d:140ms">
          <Card class="p-7">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <!-- Founder photo goes here (replace the initials circle) -->
              <span class="grid h-14 w-14 shrink-0 place-items-center rounded-full bg-navy font-display text-lg font-bold text-white">C.n.l</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-navy">The Founder</p>
                <p class="text-sm text-navy/55">Click.n.likes</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-5 text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-navy/75">
              "Nine years in, my rule has not changed: build the growth asset, not the dependency. If it stops working
              the day you stop paying, it was never yours."
            </p>
            <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 border-t border-navy/10 pt-5 text-sm">
              <span><b class="font-display text-navy">9 yrs</b> <span class="text-navy/55">building organic growth</span></span>
              <span><b class="font-display text-navy">Every</b> <span class="text-navy/55">industry, tailored</span></span>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mid-page CTA -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-[5vw] py-12">
    <InlineCta
      eyebrow="No dependency, just growth you own"
      title="Curious what an owned growth asset looks like for your business?"
      primaryLabel="Talk to a strategist"
      secondaryLabel="Scan my site free"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- How we work -->
  <section class="border-t border-navy/10">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-[5vw] py-16">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
        <p class="reveal text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] text-navy/50 uppercase">How we work</p>
        <h2 class="reveal mt-3 font-display text-[clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.4rem)] leading-[1.12] font-bold text-navy" style="--d:80ms">
          No sugarcoating. Just what's working and what isn't.
        </h2>
        <p class="reveal mt-4 text-lg text-navy/70" style="--d:140ms">
          And one number we report that most agencies don't: not just revenue, but <b class="text-navy">profit</b>. A
          ₹50,000 month means nothing if it costs ₹60,000 to generate it, so every report breaks out what a result was
          actually worth after cost, not just the traffic or revenue headline.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10 grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-3">
        <Card class="reveal" style="--d:0ms">
          <div class="mb-4 grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-teal/10 text-teal-dark"><MessageSquare size={20} stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" /></div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-navy">Fundamentals, not fads</h3>
          <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-navy/60">Built on how people search and how trust compounds, not the algorithm update of the month.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card class="reveal" style="--d:90ms">
          <div class="mb-4 grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-teal/10 text-teal-dark"><Layers size={20} stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" /></div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-navy">Built for you, not a template</h3>
          <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-navy/60">Sometimes a full SEO and content build, sometimes consulting your team on what to fix. Always specific to your business.</p>
        </Card>
        <Card class="reveal" style="--d:180ms">
          <div class="mb-4 grid h-11 w-11 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-teal/10 text-teal-dark"><Clock size={20} stroke-width={2} aria-hidden="true" /></div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-navy">Honest timelines</h3>
          <p class="mt-1.5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-navy/60">Organic compounds, it does not switch on overnight. We tell you that upfront, every time.</p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Clients -->
  <section class="border-t border-navy/10 bg-off">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-[5vw] py-14">
      <p class="reveal text-center text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] text-navy/40 uppercase">Trusted across industries</p>
      <div class="reveal mt-7" style="--d:80ms"><ClientLogos gridCols="grid-cols-3 sm:grid-cols-5" /></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact form -->
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-[5vw] py-16 text-center">
    <p class="reveal text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.14em] text-navy/50 uppercase">Let's talk</p>
    <h2 class="reveal mt-3 font-display text-[clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.4rem)] leading-[1.12] font-bold text-navy" style="--d:80ms">
      Ready to build growth you actually own?
    </h2>
    <div class="reveal mt-8" style="--d:160ms">
      <SimpleForm
        client:visible
        tag="about"
        fields={formFields}
        submitLabel="Talk to us"
        contactHref={withBase('/contact/')}
        toolsHref={withBase('/tools/')}
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
